        <Parent_String>military museums (buildings) [300005826], history museums (buildings) [300243189], museums buildings by subject [300169788], museums (buildings) [300005768], exhibition buildings [300005748], single built works by function [300004894], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
